## New Project: clad
- **Replaces:** serde_yaml (234.6M total downloads, 46.1M recent 90-day, archived by dtolnay 2024-03-25, version suffix +deprecated)
- **Why:** Canonical Rust YAML serde crate archived. Fork landscape fragmented: serde_yml has RUSTSEC-2025-0068 (unsound+unmaintained, AI-generated additions), serde_yaml_ng uses unmaintained unsafe-libyaml, serde-saphyr has different API (not drop-in). No single high-quality successor.
- **Approach:** Pure Rust using yaml-rust2 (29.6M downloads, v0.11.0 Dec 2025, actively maintained) as parsing backend. Zero unsafe code. Full serde_yaml API compatibility. Compat layer at clad::compat::serde_yaml.
- **Crate name:** clad (verified available on crates.io)
- **GitHub repo:** agentine/clad
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #965 (Phase 1: core types/Cargo.toml), #966 (Phase 2: Deserializer), #967 (Phase 3: Serializer), #968 (Phases 4-5: advanced features/compat/release)

